flow-state|physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange|strength_1|1|Starting through movement|You can often enter the work by changing pace, moving your body, or doing something practical. This helps attention arrive without forcing it.|physical_rhythm|active|flow-state::physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange::strength_1
flow-state|physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange|strength_2|2|Turning energy into careful work|Once attention is engaged, you can use focus to stay with the part that matters. This helps motion become useful progress rather than activity for its own sake.|deep_focus|active|flow-state::physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange::strength_2
flow-state|physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange|strength_3|3|Refreshing the rhythm|When action starts to feel too repetitive, new angles can help you adjust the route. This keeps the work responsive without losing its practical base.|creative_movement|active|flow-state::physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange::strength_3
