13_Application
domain_key|pattern_key|application_area|guidance_type|priority|guidance_text|linked_signal_key|status|lookup_key
flow-state|physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange|use_this_when|guidance|1|Use this pattern when the work feels stuck, flat, or too mental. Change pace, walk, practise, make, sort, or work with a simple rhythm before trying to solve it by thinking harder.|physical_rhythm|active|flow-state::physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange::use_this_when
flow-state|physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange|watch_for|guidance|2|Watch for the moment when movement has done its job and the work now needs a pause. That is often the point to focus, choose, or ask one useful person what is clear.|deep_focus|active|flow-state::physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange::watch_for
flow-state|physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange|develop_by|guidance|3|Develop by building a clear pause into the rhythm. Use that pause to choose the next step, refine the result, or test it with someone before moving again.|social_exchange|active|flow-state::physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange::develop_by
14_Closing_Integration
domain_key|pattern_key|score_shape|closing_summary|core_gift|core_trap|development_edge|memorable_line|status|lookup_key
flow-state|physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange|concentrated|This result points to a flow style built around movement, then focus. You are likely to do your best work when pace, rhythm, or physical engagement helps attention start, then focus, ideas, and outside testing help the work become clear and useful.|Your gift is the ability to use movement and rhythm to access attention, energy, and progress.|The trap is staying in action after the work needs stillness, feedback, or a clear decision.|The useful edge is to pause at the right time so movement can turn into focused progress.|Move first. Then pause where the work needs your full attention.|active|flow-state::physical_rhythm_deep_focus_creative_movement_social_exchange::concentrated
